1928;;So This Is Love?;;American;;Frank Capra;;Shirley Mason, William Collier Jr.;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/So_This_Is_Love%3F_(film);;Jerry McGuire (William Collier Jr.) is a dress designer who is tired of being looked upon as a wimp. He begins secretly training as a boxer to take on Spike Mullins (Johnnie Walker) and win the affections of store clerk Hilda Jensen (Shirley Mason).[2]